<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1104541-i-want-to-start-to-read-this-book-how-was">I want to start to read this book, how was it?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1104541'><a id="like_count_community_question_1104541" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1104541?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">39 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F32388712-the-ministry-of-utmost-happiness">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1104541-i-want-to-start-to-read-this-book-how-was">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1104541-i-want-to-start-to-read-this-book-how-was">See all 15 answers</a>
